posts.subject: ZeroTalk
posts.body:
ZeroTalk is possibly the largest ZeroNet english language forum. The site is searchable thru [ZeroHello](/) newsfeed "Search in connected sites".

Forum support:
- [markdown formating](https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Cheatsheet) of the text.
- Muting of spamming users (three dots menu when mouse hover).
- subscribing to new comments added to favorite discussion topics (via [ZeroHello](/) newsfeed
